      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "Why does it have to look like that? (1) If I am creating my own proprietary exception, I will make it package-private (or private if it is not top-level).  (2) Same thing wrt to the constructors.  (3) I won&#39;t define 4 constructors unless I need them."
    }, {
