    "body" : "<p>You can create you own exception by inheriting from <code>java.lang.Exception</code> \n<a href=\"http://www.seasite.niu.edu/cs580java/testexception.htm\" rel=\"nofollow\">Here</a> is an example that can help you do that.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "comments" : [ {
      "owner" : {
        "account_id" : 366776,
        "reputation" : 7184,
